{"tid":1989504,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳宗憲護航羅志祥: 年輕愛玩不見得做錯事","createTime":"2020-04-26T04:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T13:56:41.000Z","uid":89543,"like":48,"dislike":396,"uniUserReply":114,"replies":[{"pid":"66a1b589163c9f047b650efd37f5570cf78801c0","tid":1989504,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2020/04/25/3145832_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2020%2F04%2F25%2F3145832_1.jpg&h=3577bf13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔記者鍾智凱／台北報導〕「亞洲舞王」羅志祥（小豬）23日遭中國網紅舊愛周揚青掀開桃色醜聞，演藝事業陷入最大危機，而主持人吳宗憲也在直播中開示此事。<br />\n<br />\n吳宗憲對此事評論為：「或許大家都愛玩，大家都年輕嘛，玩心還很重，但不見得真的有做錯什麼事情，我不敢太過直接評斷，我沒有在現場。小豬加油！對於我來講，我在台灣就是透明人，對於我失去的自由蠻感傷的，這一大段時間也會受到很多攻擊，成也蕭何，敗也蕭何，我心中沒有怨言。」"},{"pid":"990b47f3923b8c0ef800b6ebcceb7917306d6b3f","tid":1989504,"uid":89543,"like":157,"dislike":0,"score":157,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:32:43.000Z","msg":"大家都是中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edab480ddda6b5afbf6463b5330dd2037768311","tid":1989504,"uid":50582,"like":372,"dislike":2,"score":370,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:33:43.000Z","msg":"都41歲啦，仲以為你真係後生咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914c7c12a970d28a7eb0ec51ea8c982711bccd8a","tid":1989504,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8922cd0a2522f020392a28b87d3a4a8aa419b47c","tid":1989504,"uid":25659,"like":48,"dislike":0,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:35:50.000Z","msg":"小豬加油屌多啲女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d34ad19c580f6ef3a678c07e8c39a58683